Source: splitvt
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50), libncurses5-dev, dpkg-dev (>= 1.9.0), hardening-wrapper
Maintainer: Mònica Ramírez Arceda <monica@debian.org>
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Vcs-Git: git://git.debian.org/collab-maint/splitvt.git
Vcs-Browser: http://git.debian.org/?p=collab-maint/splitvt.git

Package: splitvt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: run two programs in a split screen
 A utility to split a vt100 compatible screen into two halves,
 upper and lower, and run a different program simultaneously
 in each half.
